IT TAKES A WHILE TO FIGURE OUT THE WALLS AIN’T GONNA MOVE,

723
00:36:52,176 --> 00:36:54,645
BUT SOONER OR LATER, YOU FIND A WAY TO GET ON WITH IT.

724
00:36:57,014 --> 00:36:58,616
[laughs]

725
00:36:58,616 --> 00:36:59,951
WHEW.

726
00:36:59,951 --> 00:37:03,621
YOU AIN’T MUCH ON SMALL TALK, ARE YOU?

727
00:37:03,621 --> 00:37:07,491
I SAVE MY SMALL TALK FOR SMALL PEOPLE.

728
00:37:15,366 --> 00:37:17,335
[exhales]

729
00:37:22,940 --> 00:37:27,211
DO YOU EVER FEEL LIKE IT’S STILL THERE,

730
00:37:27,211 --> 00:37:30,247
YOU KNOW, WHEN YOU’RE LYING IN YOUR BED

731
00:37:30,247 --> 00:37:34,218
OR WHEN YOU JUST FORGET YOURSELF?

732
00:37:34,218 --> 00:37:37,321
SOMETIMES THE FEELING COMES BACK.

733
00:37:37,321 --> 00:37:39,724
THAT’S WHAT I THOUGHT.

734
00:37:39,724 --> 00:37:46,097
I THINK, WHEN YOU LOSE A PART OF YOURSELF LIKE THAT,

735
00:37:46,097 --> 00:37:48,466
SOMETHING STILL STAYS WITH YOU FOREVER.

736
00:37:50,468 --> 00:37:53,070
YEAH, YEAH, I GUESS YOU’RE RIGHT.

737
00:38:05,883 --> 00:38:09,253
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU SHOULD DO?

738
00:38:09,253 --> 00:38:11,222
WHAT?

739
00:38:13,224 --> 00:38:15,059
YOU SHOULD TAKE ME OUT TO THE PRAIRIE

740
00:38:15,059 --> 00:38:17,695
AND MAKE LOVE TO ME.

741
00:38:20,031 --> 00:38:22,033
[gunshot and glass shattering]

742
00:38:22,033 --> 00:38:23,467
HA!

743
00:38:25,703 --> 00:38:27,171
YOUR TURN.

744
00:38:40,051 --> 00:38:41,585
WANT TO SWITCH RIFLES AGAIN?

745
00:38:41,585 --> 00:38:43,721
NO, I DON’T.

746
00:38:48,726 --> 00:38:50,027
THANK YOU.

747
00:38:53,064 --> 00:38:55,733
I SEE YOU OVER THERE, BOY.

748
00:38:55,733 --> 00:38:58,703
IT’S TIME YOU LEARNED HOW TO FIRE A RIFLE.

749
00:38:58,703 --> 00:39:00,738
COME HERE, SPARTA.

750
00:39:00,738 --> 00:39:04,742
COME ON, LET’S GIVE IT A TRY.

751
00:39:04,742 --> 00:39:06,610
LET’S GO.

752
00:39:06,610 --> 00:39:08,979
ALL RIGHT, THIS WILL BE FUN.

753
00:39:08,979 --> 00:39:11,415
COME ON, GET UP HERE.

754
00:39:11,415 --> 00:39:12,883
ALL RIGHT, FIRST OFF,

755
00:39:12,883 --> 00:39:15,152
GET A GOOD STANCE, LIKE THAT, ALL RIGHT?

756
00:39:15,152 --> 00:39:18,789
NOW, WHENEVER ANYBODY HANDS YOU A GUN,

757
00:39:18,789 --> 00:39:20,958
YOU ALWAYS ASSUME THAT IT’S LOADED.

758
00:39:20,958 --> 00:39:22,526
YOU DON’T PUT YOUR FINGER ON THE TRIGGER

759
00:39:22,526 --> 00:39:24,462
UNTIL YOU’RE READY TO FIRE, OKAY?

760
00:39:24,462 --> 00:39:25,930
NOW, DON’T HOLD HER TOO TIGHT,

761
00:39:25,930 --> 00:39:27,565
OR ELSE SHE’LL SHAKE WHEN YOU GO TO FIRE.

762
00:39:27,565 --> 00:39:30,801
OKAY, AND JUST RELAX.

763
00:39:30,801 --> 00:39:34,004
RELAX, OR ELSE YOU’RE GONNA MISS YOUR TARGET.

764
00:39:34,004 --> 00:39:37,041
OKAY, GET SOMETHING IN YOUR SIGHT.

765
00:39:39,844 --> 00:39:41,846
OPEN YOUR EYES UP.

766
00:39:41,846 --> 00:39:43,547
YOU GOT TO SEE YOUR TARGET.

767
00:39:43,547 --> 00:39:45,983
WHAT IF THAT WAS A DEER

768
00:39:45,983 --> 00:39:49,053
OR A BIRD OR SOMETHING, AND IT’S MOVING?

769
00:39:49,053 --> 00:39:50,888
ALL RIGHT.

770
00:39:50,888 --> 00:39:54,692
NOW, HOLD YOUR BREATH.

771
00:39:54,692 --> 00:39:56,894
OKAY, I’M GONNA COCK THE GUN FOR YA.

772
00:39:56,894 --> 00:40:01,565
[gun clicks]

773
00:40:01,565 --> 00:40:03,801
AND SQUEEZE THE TRIGGER.

774
00:40:06,570 --> 00:40:08,506
FIRE.

775
00:40:10,508 --> 00:40:13,344
FIRE.

776
00:40:13,344 --> 00:40:14,912
GOD DAMN IT, FIRE.

777
00:40:14,912 --> 00:40:16,580
[gunshot]

778
00:40:25,556 --> 00:40:28,259
I JUST DON’T KNOW WHERE I WENT WRONG WITH THAT BOY.

779
00:40:29,527 --> 00:40:30,995
WELL...

780
00:40:30,995 --> 00:40:32,997
YOU KNOW HE NEEDS A HUG FROM HIS MOTHER

781
00:40:32,997 --> 00:40:35,533
JUST TO GET THE COURAGE TO BREATHE.

782
00:40:35,533 --> 00:40:37,301
SOMETIMES IT SEEMS LIKE HE’S AFRAID

783
00:40:37,301 --> 00:40:39,069
OF JUST ABOUT EVERYTHING.

784
00:40:41,806 --> 00:40:43,407
ALL I WANTED OUT OF THIS LIFE

785
00:40:43,407 --> 00:40:45,543
WAS A SON I COULD TAKE HUNTING AND FISHING.

786
00:40:45,543 --> 00:40:49,013
YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENED THE LAST TIME WE WENT FISHING?

787
00:40:49,013 --> 00:40:51,916
I WENT TO BAIT WITH A LIVE NIGHT CRAWLER,

788
00:40:51,916 --> 00:40:54,018
AND HE UPS AND STARTS SCREAMING AND CRYING,

789
00:40:54,018 --> 00:40:56,887
AND HE BEGS ME NOT TO PUT IT ON A HOOK.

790
00:40:56,887 --> 00:41:00,024
IT’S THERE CORKSCREWING IN MY HAND,

791
00:41:00,024 --> 00:41:01,859
AND HE’S OVER THERE CRYING OVER IT,

792
00:41:01,859 --> 00:41:03,928
CRYING OVER A WORM.

793
00:41:06,464 --> 00:41:08,532
I’VE LOST A LOT OF SLEEP OVER IT,

794
00:41:08,532 --> 00:41:10,935
AND I STILL CAN’T FIGURE OUT

795
00:41:10,935 --> 00:41:13,404
HOW HE GOT SO GODDANG SENSITIVE.

796
00:41:13,404 --> 00:41:15,873
AND I TELL MARY JOAN NOT TO PUT UP WITH IT.

797
00:41:15,873 --> 00:41:17,508
SHE’S BEEN TO THAT WOMAN’S COLLEGE,

798
00:41:17,508 --> 00:41:19,610
AND SHE READ ALL THEM CHILD PSYCHOLOGY BOOKS,

799
00:41:19,610 --> 00:41:22,546
SO SHE THINKS SHE KNOWS EVERYTHING ABOUT EVERYTHING.

800
00:41:25,382 --> 00:41:28,152
IT AIN’T EVEN LIKE HAVING A SON.

801
00:41:28,152 --> 00:41:30,321
OH, YOU’RE WRONG THERE, ZACH.

802
00:41:30,321 --> 00:41:32,156
YOU’RE WRONG.

803
00:41:32,156 --> 00:41:34,124
HE’S A FINE BOY.

804
00:41:34,124 --> 00:41:36,527
YOU OUGHT TO BE PROUD OF HIM.

805
00:41:36,527 --> 00:41:39,597
HE’LL STRAIGHTEN UP.

806
00:41:39,597 --> 00:41:41,565
HE’LL TURN OUT JUST FINE.

807
00:41:43,834 --> 00:41:46,837
BESIDES, THERE’S MORE TO LIFE THAN BAITING A HOOK

808
00:41:46,837 --> 00:41:48,873
OR SHOOTING A DANG GUN.

809
00:41:48,873 --> 00:41:50,574
NO, BUT IT’S A SYMPTOM.

810
00:41:50,574 --> 00:41:52,109
IT’S A SYMPTOM.

811
00:41:52,109 --> 00:41:56,513
YOU KNOW HOW SHARP LIFE’S TEETH ARE.

812
00:41:56,513 --> 00:42:00,117
I JUST DON’T WANT TO SEE MY BOY EATEN UP, THAT’S ALL.

813
00:42:02,653 --> 00:42:05,556
[gunshot]

814
00:42:05,556 --> 00:42:07,391
(Sparta) HEY, PARTNER.

815
00:42:08,859 --> 00:42:10,995
HOP IN.

816
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:26,410
THAT GUN SCARES YOU, DON’T IT?

817
00:42:26,410 --> 00:42:28,679
BUT THE GUN CAN’T SHOOT ITSELF.

818
00:42:28,679 --> 00:42:31,315
SOMEBODY’S GOT TO PULL THE TRIGGER, DON’T THEY?

819
00:42:33,050 --> 00:42:35,953
THEN IT AIN’T THE GUN THAT’S GOT YOU SCARED, IS IT?

820
00:42:38,222 --> 00:42:40,691
SO WHAT ALL YOU THINK YOU MIGHT DO ABOUT IT?

821
00:42:43,093 --> 00:42:44,528
[gunshot]

822
00:42:44,528 --> 00:42:46,030
WHOO.

823
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:48,198
(Zach) I THINK YOU OWE ME ANOTHER DOLLAR.

824
00:42:51,969 --> 00:42:53,337
[crickets chirping]

825
00:42:53,337 --> 00:42:54,672
(Crawford) LET’S SEE,

826
00:42:54,672 --> 00:42:57,207
"MY ESTATE...

827
00:42:57,207 --> 00:43:00,945
"ALL STRUCTURES, FURNITURE, AND ARTICLES THEREIN

828
00:43:00,945 --> 00:43:02,680
GO TO MY WIFE MURTIS."

829
00:43:02,680 --> 00:43:04,014
[sobs]

830
00:43:04,014 --> 00:43:05,582
(Zach) IT’S ALL RIGHT, MA.

831
00:43:05,582 --> 00:43:09,720
"TO MY SON, ZACHARY WHIT, I BEQUEATH

832
00:43:09,720 --> 00:43:13,357
"THE AMOUNT OF $15,000,

833
00:43:13,357 --> 00:43:15,659
"WHICH I ASSUME HE WILL USE

834
00:43:15,659 --> 00:43:18,595
TO PURCHASE A CADILLAC AUTOMOBILE."

835
00:43:18,595 --> 00:43:20,998
"MAY HE FINALLY SHUT THE HELL UP ABOUT IT

836
00:43:20,998 --> 00:43:23,100
AND GET ON WITH LIVING."

837
00:43:23,100 --> 00:43:25,169
[chuckles]

838
00:43:25,169 --> 00:43:28,906
"TO MY DAUGHTER MIRANDA,

839
00:43:28,906 --> 00:43:31,475
"WHOSE DELICATE NATURE

840
00:43:31,475 --> 00:43:33,744
"HAS REQUIRED INSTITUTIONALIZATION,

841
00:43:33,744 --> 00:43:37,147
"I HAVE SET UP A TRUST OF $15,000

842
00:43:37,147 --> 00:43:39,616
"FOR THE DAY WHEN HER PHYSICIANS

843
00:43:39,616 --> 00:43:42,219
"DEEM HER READY TO REENTER SOCIETY,

844
00:43:42,219 --> 00:43:43,887
"GOD WILLING.

845
00:43:43,887 --> 00:43:46,090
"TO SPARTA,

846
00:43:46,090 --> 00:43:48,759
"MY GRANDSON AND NAMESAKE,

847
00:43:48,759 --> 00:43:50,327
I BEQUEATH MY GUN COLLECTION."

848
00:43:50,327 --> 00:43:51,762
[Zach whispering] HEY, HOW ABOUT THAT?

849
00:43:51,762 --> 00:43:53,731
"MAY HE PROUDLY DISPLAY IT

850
00:43:53,731 --> 00:43:55,299
"AND FOREVER CHERISH THE VALUES

851
00:43:55,299 --> 00:43:57,534
"AND THE PEOPLES IT HELPED TO DEFEND.

852
00:43:57,534 --> 00:43:59,069
"AND FINALLY,

853
00:43:59,069 --> 00:44:01,505
"TO MY NEPHEW CLINTON,

854
00:44:01,505 --> 00:44:03,474
"WHO WAS BORN AND BRED IN THE LUXURY

855
00:44:03,474 --> 00:44:06,076
"OF MY BROTHER’S OIL DYNASTY,

856
00:44:06,076 --> 00:44:09,446
"I DO NOT TRY TO LEAVE ANY MONETARY INHERITANCE,

857
00:44:09,446 --> 00:44:15,452
"WHICH WOULD TRULY SEEM AS INFINITESIMAL AS DROPS THE OCEAN.

858
00:44:15,452 --> 00:44:17,888
"INSTEAD, I BEQUEATH TO HIM

859
00:44:17,888 --> 00:44:21,859
"MY SECRET BARBECUE AND BEEF JERKY RECIPES.

860
00:44:21,859 --> 00:44:26,163
"MAY HE SAVOR THE TASTE AND REMEMBER HIS SUMMERS

861
00:44:26,163 --> 00:44:28,265
VISITING US ON THE FARM."

862
00:44:28,265 --> 00:44:30,200
[Zach whispering] DAD’S SAUCE.

863
00:44:30,200 --> 00:44:33,003
(Crawford) "REGARDING ROBERT E. LEE,

864
00:44:33,003 --> 00:44:35,572
"THE LAST OF THE DESERT WARRIOR STEEDS,

865
00:44:35,572 --> 00:44:38,842
"UPON HIS DEATH, RATHER THAN HAVING

866
00:44:38,842 --> 00:44:41,678
"HIS HEAD MOUNTED IN THE BARN WITH HIS ANCESTORS,

867
00:44:41,678 --> 00:44:45,682
"I REQUEST THAT HE BE BURIED IN THE PLOT

868
00:44:45,682 --> 00:44:48,952
SOUTH OF MY GRAVE, THE NORTH BEING RESERVED FOR MURTIS."

869
00:44:54,591 --> 00:44:57,428
THERE’S A CODICIL TO THE WILL.

870
00:44:57,428 --> 00:44:59,596
"TO WALTER FOLEY,

871
00:44:59,596 --> 00:45:03,534
"THE SON OF OTIS FOLEY,

872
00:45:03,534 --> 00:45:06,303
"I BEQUEATH THE ENCLOSED LETTERS

873
00:45:06,303 --> 00:45:09,106
"ENTRUSTED TO MY ATTORNEY,

874
00:45:09,106 --> 00:45:11,675
J.W. CROFT."

875
00:45:11,675 --> 00:45:12,976
THERE YOU GO, WALTER.

876
00:45:12,976 --> 00:45:14,778
(Walter) THANK YOU.

877
00:45:19,883 --> 00:45:21,652
IT’S A LETTER FROM THE DEAN

878
00:45:21,652 --> 00:45:25,422
OF MY MEDICAL SCHOOL AT LA GRANGE.

879
00:45:25,422 --> 00:45:27,725
IT’S A...

880
00:45:27,725 --> 00:45:31,295
WELL, IT-- IT’S A FULL SCHOLARSHIP.

881
00:45:31,295 --> 00:45:33,831
AND THERE’S A CHECK HERE, TOO.

882
00:45:33,831 --> 00:45:36,133
(Crawford) PRECISELY.

883
00:45:36,133 --> 00:45:39,736
"I LEAVE WALTER FOLEY THE SUM OF $10,000,

884
00:45:39,736 --> 00:45:42,372
"SUCH CAPITAL TO BE USED

885
00:45:42,372 --> 00:45:44,808
IN THE ESTABLISHING OF HIS FIRST PRACTICE."

886
00:45:44,808 --> 00:45:46,176
WHY?

887
00:45:46,176 --> 00:45:48,178
WHY IS HE GIVING ALL THIS TO ME?

888
00:45:48,178 --> 00:45:51,315
DOES OLD SPARTA SAY WHY HE GIVES THE BOY THE MONEY?

889
00:45:54,651 --> 00:45:56,987
"IT IS WITH UNSPEAKABLE REMORSE...

890
00:45:59,723 --> 00:46:01,558
"THAT I CONFESS

891
00:46:01,558 --> 00:46:04,394
"TO THE SHOOTING OF HIS FATHER, OTIS FOLEY,

892
00:46:04,394 --> 00:46:06,964
MANY YEARS AGO."

893
00:46:06,964 --> 00:46:09,967
[Otis gasping]

894
00:46:14,838 --> 00:46:19,309
(Crawford) "THE MURDER OF OTIS FOLEY

895
00:46:19,309 --> 00:46:22,179
"HAS HAUNTED ME FOR YEARS.

896
00:46:22,179 --> 00:46:26,683
"ALTHOUGH I REALIZE NOTHING CAN EVER MAKE UP

897
00:46:26,683 --> 00:46:29,987
"FOR THE LOSS OF HIS FATHER, I HOPE MY CONTRIBUTION

898
00:46:29,987 --> 00:46:32,823
"TO WALTER’S LIFESAVING PROFESSION...

899
00:46:35,159 --> 00:46:38,362
"WILL HELP TEMPER THE PAIN

900
00:46:38,362 --> 00:46:40,230
AND THE BITTERNESS."

901
00:46:41,765 --> 00:46:44,201
DID HE SAY-- DID HE SAY WHY?

902
00:46:44,201 --> 00:46:45,736
I DON’T BELIEVE IT.

903
00:46:45,736 --> 00:46:48,906
MAMA, HOW COULD DADDY BE A MURDERER?

904
00:46:48,906 --> 00:46:50,307
(Walter) IF YOU’LL ALL EXCUSE ME NOW.

905
00:46:50,307 --> 00:46:51,642
I THINK I’LL BE GOING.

906
00:46:51,642 --> 00:46:53,243
(Zach) WALTER.

907
00:46:53,243 --> 00:46:55,512
(Mary Joan) LITTLE SPARTA.

908
00:46:55,512 --> 00:46:57,214
I JUST DON’T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.

909
00:46:57,214 --> 00:47:00,117
NEITHER DO I, ZACH.

910
00:47:00,117 --> 00:47:02,119
MURTIS...

911
00:47:02,119 --> 00:47:03,954
WALTER.

912
00:47:03,954 --> 00:47:05,756
THANK YOU FOR SUPPER.

913
00:47:07,424 --> 00:47:09,459
♪

914
00:47:18,936 --> 00:47:20,270
WHOA, WAIT A SECOND.

915
00:47:20,270 --> 00:47:22,472
HANG ON A SECOND, PARTNER.

916
00:47:22,472 --> 00:47:24,141
HEY, HEY, HEY.

917
00:47:26,276 --> 00:47:28,779
I KILLED HIM, ’CAUSE I THOUGHT HE WAS TRYING

918
00:47:28,779 --> 00:47:30,480
TO STEAL YOUR GRANDMA AWAY FROM ME.

919
00:47:32,683 --> 00:47:34,351
[sighs]

920
00:47:34,351 --> 00:47:39,957
I WAS CAUGHT UP IN AN UNCONTROLLABLE JEALOUS RAGE.

921
00:47:39,957 --> 00:47:41,758
JEALOUSY AIN’T GREEN, BOY.

922
00:47:41,758 --> 00:47:46,697
IT’S RED, LIKE A RED-HOT POKER.

923
00:47:46,697 --> 00:47:50,634
YOU’LL UNDERSTAND SOMEDAY WHEN YOU TAKE A WIFE.

924
00:47:50,634 --> 00:47:52,836
WHOA.

925
00:47:52,836 --> 00:47:54,972
[Murtis moaning]

926
00:47:54,972 --> 00:47:58,542
I COULD SUCK IT ALL DAY LONG, OTIS.

927
00:47:58,542 --> 00:48:01,411
(Otis) YOU CAN SUCK IT AS LONG AS YOU WANT TO, MRS. WHIT.

928
00:48:08,085 --> 00:48:11,255
WHERE--WHERE ARE YOU? OH, GOD, NO!

929
00:48:11,255 --> 00:48:12,923
(Sparta) EVERYBODY KNEW I DID IT,

930
00:48:12,923 --> 00:48:16,126
BUT NOBODY EVER COME AFTER ME, ’CAUSE OTIS WAS BLACK,

931
00:48:16,126 --> 00:48:18,028
AND I THINK THEY WERE ALL RELIEVED

932
00:48:18,028 --> 00:48:19,763
I DIDN’T SHOOT YOUR GRANDMA, TOO.

933
00:48:19,763 --> 00:48:21,932
I NEVER LET ANY OF IT BOTHER ME MUCH,

934
00:48:21,932 --> 00:48:24,735
UNTIL A WHILE AGO, WHEN I GOT THIS DREAM.

935
00:48:36,813 --> 00:48:39,416
OTIS?

936
00:48:50,527 --> 00:48:55,032
[screams]

937
00:48:55,032 --> 00:48:57,434
ON THE BY AND BY, A GLIMPSE OF REDEMPTION

938
00:48:57,434 --> 00:48:59,236
CAME INTO MY SOUL,

939
00:48:59,236 --> 00:49:01,638
I REALIZED THERE WAS NEVER ANYTHING I COULD DO

940
00:49:01,638 --> 00:49:04,274
TO BRING OTIS BACK, BUT I COULD SURE HELP HIS SON, WALTER.

941
00:49:04,274 --> 00:49:06,543
YES, SIR, THAT I SURELY COULD DO.

942
00:49:06,543 --> 00:49:09,646
YOU SEE, IF YOU DON’T UNTANGLE

943
00:49:09,646 --> 00:49:12,716
ALL OF THESE LONG, DARK, LOOSE THREADS IN LIFE,

944
00:49:12,716 --> 00:49:15,485
THEY’LL ALL COME TOGETHER

945
00:49:15,485 --> 00:49:18,422
AND FORM A NOOSE AROUND YOUR SOUL AT THE END.

946
00:49:20,624 --> 00:49:23,560
[sobbing]

947
00:49:34,004 --> 00:49:36,573
[sobbing]

948
00:49:45,415 --> 00:49:47,818
MIRANDA.

949
00:49:47,818 --> 00:49:49,152
YEAH?

950
00:49:49,152 --> 00:49:51,288
GO BACK TO THE HOUSE!

951
00:50:05,435 --> 00:50:07,371
MIRANDA...

952
00:50:07,371 --> 00:50:11,141
MIRANDA, WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

953
00:50:36,199 --> 00:50:38,702
[camel groaning]

954
00:50:41,705 --> 00:50:43,907
(Zach) IS HE GONNA GET BETTER?

955
00:50:43,907 --> 00:50:46,309
WALK ME TO MY CAR, ZACH.

956
00:50:50,981 --> 00:50:54,251
ANIMALS HAVE GOT TO WANT TO LIVE.

957
00:50:54,251 --> 00:50:56,987
ROBERT E. IS JUST READY TO--

958
00:50:56,987 --> 00:50:59,356
HE’S READY TO PASS ON.

959
00:51:02,225 --> 00:51:04,327
COME ON, NOW, HONEY.

960
00:51:04,327 --> 00:51:06,062
IT’S ALL RIGHT, REALLY.

961
00:51:06,062 --> 00:51:08,265
DADDY’S GONNA TAKE CARE OF IT.

962
00:51:12,335 --> 00:51:14,504
HONEY?

963
00:51:14,504 --> 00:51:16,406
SPARTA!

964
00:51:16,406 --> 00:51:18,241
[gun clicks]

965
00:51:22,546 --> 00:51:23,980
OH, LORD.

966
00:51:29,419 --> 00:51:30,787
COME ON, SON.

967
00:51:30,787 --> 00:51:32,355
YOU GOT TO GO WITH YOUR MOTHER.

968
00:51:32,355 --> 00:51:33,657
NOW, GO ON.

969
00:51:33,657 --> 00:51:36,159
ROBERT E. IS IN PAIN, SON.

970
00:51:36,159 --> 00:51:37,727
HE’S IN PAIN,

971
00:51:37,727 --> 00:51:39,496
AND WE GOT TO LET HIM GO.

972
00:51:39,496 --> 00:51:41,031
SPARTA,

973
00:51:41,031 --> 00:51:43,033
WE’VE GOT TO RELEASE HIM

974
00:51:43,033 --> 00:51:44,267
AND LET HIM GO TO HEAVEN.

975
00:51:44,267 --> 00:51:45,669
LOOK AT HIM, SPARTA. LOOK AT HIM.

976
00:51:45,669 --> 00:51:47,771
[groans]

977
00:51:47,771 --> 00:51:49,005
SPARTA, I GOT TO DO IT.

978
00:51:49,005 --> 00:51:50,774
YOU CAN DO WHAT YOU GOT TO DO LATER.

979
00:51:52,442 --> 00:51:53,777
BUT I GOT TO PUT HIM--

980
00:51:53,777 --> 00:51:56,079
LATER.

981
00:51:58,148 --> 00:52:00,784
[grunts]

982
00:52:00,784 --> 00:52:03,186
ALL RIGHT, SPARTA, YOU CAN STAY.

983
00:52:03,186 --> 00:52:06,957
THERE’S NO POINT IN YOU GALS STAYING UP.

984
00:52:06,957 --> 00:52:09,893
CLINTON AND I GOT TO BUILD A COFFIN FOR HIM.

985
00:52:09,893 --> 00:52:11,695
ALL RIGHT.

986
00:52:11,695 --> 00:52:13,897
COME ON, LET’S LEAVE THEM ALONE.

987
00:52:13,897 --> 00:52:15,599
GOOD NIGHT, LITTLE MAN.

988
00:52:19,169 --> 00:52:22,739
FUNNY HOW THINGS HAPPEN IN THREES.

989
00:52:22,739 --> 00:52:24,808
WHAT?

990
00:52:24,808 --> 00:52:27,978
THINGS IN LIFE, GOOD AND BAD, JUST SEEM TO COME IN THREES.

991
00:52:27,978 --> 00:52:29,679
FIRST OLD SPARTA DIES.

992
00:52:29,679 --> 00:52:32,182
THEN WE FIND OUT HE’S A MURDERER,

993
00:52:32,182 --> 00:52:33,950
AND NOW, ROBERT E.

994
00:52:33,950 --> 00:52:35,385
YOU KNOW, THREE IS A BIBLICAL NUMBER--

995
00:52:35,385 --> 00:52:36,920
FATHER, SON, HOLY GHOST.

996
00:52:36,920 --> 00:52:39,623
GOSH, I NEVER MUCH NOTICED.

997
00:52:43,860 --> 00:52:46,429
MARY JOAN, DO YOU THINK THAT WHEN BAD THINGS HAPPEN TO US,

998
00:52:46,429 --> 00:52:47,998
IT’S BECAUSE GOD IS PUNISHING US

999
00:52:47,998 --> 00:52:49,866
FOR WHAT WE’VE DONE?

1000
00:52:51,902 --> 00:52:54,471
WELL, YES, I THINK THERE’S A SCALE OF JUSTICE

1001
00:52:54,471 --> 00:52:56,173
IN THE UNIVERSE.

1002
00:53:04,581 --> 00:53:06,349
I’M SO--I OUGHT TO PICK THAT UP.

1003
00:53:08,718 --> 00:53:12,055
CHARLOTTE, IT’S JUST AN OLD PLATE.

1004
00:53:12,055 --> 00:53:14,090
NO, I WANT-- HONEY, GIVE ME THE PLATE.

1005
00:53:14,090 --> 00:53:15,659
I JUST--’CAUSE I-- BECAUSE I DROPPED IT.

1006
00:53:15,659 --> 00:53:17,227
HONEY, I’M GONNA TAKE THIS.

1007
00:53:17,227 --> 00:53:18,495
[sobbing]

1008
00:53:18,495 --> 00:53:19,930
CHARLOTTE, WHAT IS IT?

1009
00:53:19,930 --> 00:53:21,665
CAN I HELP YOU?

1010
00:53:21,665 --> 00:53:23,300
[sobbing]

1011
00:53:23,300 --> 00:53:25,035
OH, HONEY, WHAT IS IT?

1012
00:53:25,035 --> 00:53:29,839
ONLY GOD CAN HELP ME, AND HE WON’T, MARY JOAN.

1013
00:53:29,839 --> 00:53:31,975
HE JUST WON’T.

1014
00:53:31,975 --> 00:53:33,810
OH, CHARLOTTE, WHAT IS IT?

1015
00:53:35,378 --> 00:53:36,947
MARY JOAN, IF I TELL YOU,

1016
00:53:36,947 --> 00:53:38,815
YOU GOT TO PROMISE NOT TO TELL.

1017
00:53:38,815 --> 00:53:40,050
YOU GOT TO PROMISE.

1018
00:53:40,050 --> 00:53:41,985
HONEY, YOU KNOW I WOULDN’T TELL

1019
00:53:41,985 --> 00:53:43,720
IF YOU DIDN’T WANT ME TO.

1020
00:53:46,823 --> 00:53:48,558
I’M BARREN.

1021
00:53:48,558 --> 00:53:50,026
OH, CHARLOTTE.

1022
00:53:50,026 --> 00:53:51,628
I’M NEVER GONNA HAVE A BABY.

1023
00:53:51,628 --> 00:53:53,330
ARE YOU SURE?

1024
00:53:53,330 --> 00:53:55,665
WE’VE BEEN TRYING FOR YEARS, BUT NOTHING.

1025
00:53:55,665 --> 00:53:57,267
WHAT DO THE DOCTORS SAY?

1026
00:53:57,267 --> 00:53:59,603
OH, THEY DON’T KNOW ANYTHING.

1027
00:53:59,603 --> 00:54:02,105
IT COULD BE CLINTON. NO.

1028
00:54:03,373 --> 00:54:05,842
IT’S ME.

1029
00:54:05,842 --> 00:54:07,377
NO, HONEY.

1030
00:54:07,377 --> 00:54:10,513
I KNOW IT’S ME.

1031
00:54:10,513 --> 00:54:12,115
I KNOW IT.

1032
00:54:12,115 --> 00:54:13,249
OH, CHARLOTTE.

1033
00:54:13,249 --> 00:54:15,051
[sobbing]

1034
00:54:18,688 --> 00:54:20,056
COME HERE.

1035
00:54:20,056 --> 00:54:21,625
SHH, HONEY.

1036
00:54:21,625 --> 00:54:24,828
I MEAN, ALL I HAD TO DO WAS GIVE CLINTON A BOY.

1037
00:54:24,828 --> 00:54:27,130
JUST GIVE HIM AN HEIR TO THE COMPANY.

1038
00:54:27,130 --> 00:54:28,765
SHH.

1039
00:54:28,765 --> 00:54:31,868
NOW HE’S SO DISGUSTED, HE HASN’T TOUCHED ME IN MONTHS.

1040
00:54:31,868 --> 00:54:33,803
OH, CHARLOTTE, SHH.

1041
00:54:33,803 --> 00:54:35,472
IT’S BECAUSE CLINTON’S DADDY

1042
00:54:35,472 --> 00:54:37,574
CHEATED OLD SPARTA OUT OF ALL THAT OIL.

1043
00:54:37,574 --> 00:54:39,709
CHARLOTTE, NO. IT IS.

1044
00:54:41,845 --> 00:54:46,483
I HAD A DREAM, A DIVINE VISION,

1045
00:54:46,483 --> 00:54:48,918
AND IN THIS DREAM, I’M RIDING A CAMEL

1046
00:54:48,918 --> 00:54:51,888
THROUGH THE PLANETS AND THE STARS,

1047
00:54:51,888 --> 00:54:54,824
AND I’M CLUTCHING MY BOY,

1048
00:54:54,824 --> 00:54:58,928
MY BEAUTIFUL BABY BOY,

1049
00:54:58,928 --> 00:55:02,499
THE BOY I’M NEVER GONNA HAVE.

1050
00:55:02,499 --> 00:55:05,402
AND I LOOK THROUGH THE EYE OF THIS NEEDLE...

1051
00:55:07,070 --> 00:55:10,473
AND I SEE ALL THOSE OIL RIGS THAT MADE US SO RICH...

1052
00:55:12,575 --> 00:55:15,345
AND I REALIZE I CAN’T RIDE MY BABY INTO THE WORLD,

1053
00:55:15,345 --> 00:55:18,181
BECAUSE CHRIST HIMSELF SAID YOU CAN’T RIDE A CAMEL

1054
00:55:18,181 --> 00:55:20,216
THROUGH THE EYE OF A NEEDLE.

1055
00:55:23,520 --> 00:55:26,423
AND THAT’S WHEN I FIGURED IT OUT--

1056
00:55:27,824 --> 00:55:30,760
THAT HE’S PUNISHING ME.

1057
00:55:33,263 --> 00:55:35,331
AND I KEEP PRAYING,

1058
00:55:37,434 --> 00:55:40,336
BUT HE DOESN’T SEEM TO HEAR.

1059
00:55:40,336 --> 00:55:43,006
OH, HONEY, YOU JUST KEEP ON PRAYING.

1060
00:55:54,451 --> 00:55:57,387
[Murtis sighs]

1061
00:56:07,263 --> 00:56:08,698
MURTIS?

1062
00:56:08,698 --> 00:56:11,534
YES, DEAR?

1063
00:56:11,534 --> 00:56:14,104
HONEY, I’M HUNTING FOR SOME SLEEPING PILLS.

1064
00:56:14,104 --> 00:56:15,972
CHARLOTTE-- SHE’S A LITTLE TENSE.

1065
00:56:15,972 --> 00:56:17,774
CERTAINLY, THERE’S A WHOLE BOTTLE

1066
00:56:17,774 --> 00:56:19,676
IN THE MEDICINE CABINET.

1067
00:56:19,676 --> 00:56:21,277
THANK YOU.

1068
00:56:21,277 --> 00:56:24,647
MURTIS, ARE YOU FEELING OKAY?

1069
00:56:24,647 --> 00:56:26,783
ONLY THING LEFT.

1070
00:56:26,783 --> 00:56:28,718
WHAT?

1071
00:56:28,718 --> 00:56:31,654
IT WAS ALL JUST A MISUNDERSTANDING.

1072
00:56:43,099 --> 00:56:44,801
FOR YEARS, I HAD TRIED

1073
00:56:44,801 --> 00:56:48,271
TO FIGHT THE AWESOME POWER OF THE WHIT EAR.

1074
00:57:12,061 --> 00:57:14,430
[moaning]

1075
00:57:14,430 --> 00:57:16,566
(Sparta) STOP IT.

1076
00:57:16,566 --> 00:57:18,101
[Murtis moaning]

1077
00:57:18,101 --> 00:57:20,970
MURTIS, STOP IT.

1078
00:57:20,970 --> 00:57:22,772
GET OFF ME.

1079
00:57:29,846 --> 00:57:32,582
FINISH YOUR BREAKFAST. GO ON, SWEETHEART.

1080
00:57:34,317 --> 00:57:39,322
(Murtis) SPARTA STOPPED SLEEPING WITH ME OUT OF--WELL, FEAR.

1081
00:57:39,322 --> 00:57:44,294
I HAD REACHED A POINT OF ABSOLUTE DESPERATION

1082
00:57:44,294 --> 00:57:48,531
WHEN THE IDEA CAME TO ME.

1083
00:57:48,531 --> 00:57:53,236
(Otis) ♪ MY LORD, JESUS CHRIST

1084
00:57:53,236 --> 00:57:54,637
TAKE IT; THERE YOU GO.

1085
00:57:54,637 --> 00:57:56,339
THERE, THAT-A-BOY.

1086
00:57:56,339 --> 00:57:59,542
(Murtis) OTIS WAS--WELL, THEY WERE POOR,

1087
00:57:59,542 --> 00:58:03,179
AND HIS WIFE HAD JUST GIVEN BIRTH TO WALTER.

1088
00:58:03,179 --> 00:58:08,484
OTIS, HOW WOULD YOU LIKE TO MAKE $20?

1089
00:58:12,288 --> 00:58:16,159
[Murtis moaning]

1090
00:58:16,159 --> 00:58:20,330
OH, I COULD SUCK IT ALL DAY LONG, OTIS.

1091
00:58:20,330 --> 00:58:23,633
YOU CAN SUCK IT AS LONG AS YOU WANT TO, MRS. WHIT.

1092
00:58:25,401 --> 00:58:26,936
WHERE--

1093
00:58:26,936 --> 00:58:28,338
NO, SPARTA. NO, DON’T!

1094
00:58:28,338 --> 00:58:29,772
GET OFF ME.

1095
00:58:29,772 --> 00:58:31,708
GET OFF!

1096
00:58:36,913 --> 00:58:38,581
[gunshot]

1097
00:58:38,581 --> 00:58:41,117
[gasping]

1098
00:58:41,117 --> 00:58:43,319
[sobbing]

1099
00:58:45,989 --> 00:58:48,358
[footsteps slowly tapping]

1100
00:59:23,259 --> 00:59:26,596
(Murtis) AND THEN, WITH OTIS’ BODY STILL WARM

1101
00:59:26,596 --> 00:59:28,831
OUT THERE IN THAT FIELD...

1102
00:59:30,767 --> 00:59:33,202
SPARTA TROMPED BACK ON UP HERE

1103
00:59:33,202 --> 00:59:35,438
AND HE TOOK ME, FORCEFULLY.

1104
00:59:35,438 --> 00:59:38,875
NO. NO.

1105
00:59:38,875 --> 00:59:40,944
NO. NO.

1106
00:59:40,944 --> 00:59:42,545
OHH.

1107
00:59:42,545 --> 00:59:46,115
OH, HE JUST GAVE ME THE BEST LOVIN’

1108
00:59:46,115 --> 00:59:48,685
I’VE EVER HAD.

1109
00:59:48,685 --> 00:59:51,888
[sighs]

1110
00:59:51,888 --> 00:59:56,893
YOU KNOW, TO THIS DAY,

1111
00:59:56,893 --> 01:00:00,797
I FEEL SHAME WHEN I THINK ABOUT IT...

1112
01:00:00,797 --> 01:00:03,433
AND A KIND OF TINGLING.

1113
01:00:05,768 --> 01:00:09,806
AND, YOU KNOW, IT’S ALL BECAUSE OF THAT DAMNED WHIT EAR.

1114
01:00:13,309 --> 01:00:15,044
YOU KNOW WHAT I’M TALKING ABOUT.

1115
01:00:15,044 --> 01:00:17,347
I’VE SEEN YOU LOOK AT ZACH THAT WAY SOMETIMES.

1116
01:00:17,347 --> 01:00:19,182
I DON’T THINK SO.

1117
01:00:19,182 --> 01:00:20,984
YOU DON’T?

1118
01:00:20,984 --> 01:00:23,486
WELL, WHAT DO YOU THINK OF IT?

1119
01:00:23,486 --> 01:00:26,923
MURTIS, HONEY,

1120
01:00:26,923 --> 01:00:30,493
I THINK IF I, UH...

1121
01:00:30,493 --> 01:00:34,664
UNDERSTOOD ANY OF THAT, I--I BELIEVE I’D BE A PERVERT.

1122
01:00:37,133 --> 01:00:39,335
[both moaning]

1123
01:00:51,180 --> 01:00:53,816
GOD, DOES THAT RELIEVE STRESS.

1124
01:00:55,418 --> 01:00:57,453
YOU’RE THE FIRST WOMAN I’VE MET THAT...

1125
01:00:57,453 --> 01:00:59,422
SMOKES DURING SEX.

1126
01:00:59,422 --> 01:01:01,491
WHY WAIT?

1127
01:01:01,491 --> 01:01:03,626
YOU REALLY ARE CRAZY, YOU KNOW THAT, MIRANDA WHIT?

1128
01:01:03,626 --> 01:01:05,161
YOU BET I AM.

1129
01:01:05,161 --> 01:01:08,431
I’M A BONA FIDE SCHIZOPHRENIC.

1130
01:01:08,431 --> 01:01:11,634
GOT ALL MY PAPERS AND SHOTS TO PROVE IT.

1131
01:01:17,507 --> 01:01:19,742
WHAT’S IT LIKE IN THAT INSTITUTION?

1132
01:01:19,742 --> 01:01:23,746
LIKE A MAN WITHOUT A DICK. DULL.

1133
01:01:23,746 --> 01:01:26,516
COME ON, DON’T BE FUNNY. I’M SERIOUS.

1134
01:01:32,955 --> 01:01:36,626
WELL, IT AIN’T LIKE ANY PLACE OR ANYTHING.

1135
01:01:36,626 --> 01:01:39,429
IT’S--

1136
01:01:39,429 --> 01:01:42,598
IT’S LIKE-- YOU KNOW THAT FEELING YOU GET SOMETIMES

1137
01:01:42,598 --> 01:01:45,968
WHEN YOU’RE SINKING TO THE BOTTOM OF THE COLDEST OCEAN

1138
01:01:45,968 --> 01:01:49,305
AND YOU’RE ALL ALONE, SUFFOCATING,

1139
01:01:49,305 --> 01:01:54,043
A MILLION POUNDS PUSHIN’ ON EVERY SQUARE INCH OF YOUR BODY?

1140
01:01:54,043 --> 01:01:56,112
WELL, SOMEONE FOUND A WAY TO TAKE THAT FEELING

1141
01:01:56,112 --> 01:01:59,882
AND TURN IT INTO A PLACE, AND THAT’S WHAT THAT INSTITUTION’S LIKE.

1142
01:02:02,452 --> 01:02:04,620
[hammer pounding]

1143
01:02:08,758 --> 01:02:11,027
OH, I DON’T NEED THAT YET.

1144
01:02:11,027 --> 01:02:13,963
YOU COULD BRACE THIS FOR ME, THOUGH.

1145
01:02:27,243 --> 01:02:29,178
[clears throat]

1146
01:02:38,421 --> 01:02:41,657
AAH! SHIT!

1147
01:02:41,657 --> 01:02:43,426
HERE, YOU WANT ME TO SHOW YOU A BETTER WAY TO THAT?

1148
01:02:43,426 --> 01:02:45,528
I KNOW HOW TO DO IT. I KNOW HOW TO DO IT.

1149
01:02:45,528 --> 01:02:47,296
EVERYONE KNOWS THE BASIC PRINCIPLES

1150
01:02:47,296 --> 01:02:49,732
OF HAMMERING, OKAY?

1151
01:02:49,732 --> 01:02:52,969
ALL YOU HAVE TO DO IS PUT THE NAIL IN,

1152
01:02:52,969 --> 01:02:54,237
AND YOU JUST--

1153
01:02:54,237 --> 01:02:57,773
SHIT! SHIT! SHIT!

1154
01:02:57,773 --> 01:03:00,943
YOU HIT THE GODDAMN NAIL IN A STRAIGHT LINE!

1155
01:03:00,943 --> 01:03:03,279
I’M JUST NO GOOD AT IT.

1156
01:03:03,279 --> 01:03:06,916
I GUESS YOU NEVER DID MUCH OF THIS KIND OF WORK GROWING UP, DID YOU?

1157
01:03:06,916 --> 01:03:08,784
SURE, I DID.

1158
01:03:11,854 --> 01:03:14,624
I WAS BUILDING THINGS ALL THE TIME WHEN I WAS A KID.

1159
01:03:14,624 --> 01:03:17,126
IT’S JUST, OF COURSE, NOW, WITH THE BUSINESS THE WAY IT IS--

1160
01:03:17,126 --> 01:03:18,895
OH, I WASN’T INSINUATING ANYTHING ABOUT IT.

1161
01:03:18,895 --> 01:03:21,864
IT’S JUST THAT WHEN A GUY GROWS UP IN A WEALTHY FAMILY,

1162
01:03:21,864 --> 01:03:25,568
HE USUALLY DOESN’T GET TO DO THE KIND OF THINGS THAT MEN USUALLY DO.

1163
01:03:27,637 --> 01:03:30,206
YOU REMEMBER VISITING ME WHEN WE WERE KIDS?

1164
01:03:30,206 --> 01:03:32,275
YEAH, AND I REMEMBER PLAYING OLD MAID IN A PARLOR

1165
01:03:32,275 --> 01:03:35,611
A HELL OF A LOT MORE THAN I DO PLAYING COWBOYS AND INDIANS IN THE WOODS.

1166
01:03:35,611 --> 01:03:40,449
NOW, WHY DON’T YOU JUST ADMIT IT, ZACH?

1167
01:03:40,449 --> 01:03:43,186
YOU’RE JEALOUS, AND YOU’VE ALWAYS BEEN JEALOUS

1168
01:03:43,186 --> 01:03:45,821
EVER SINCE MY DADDY STRUCK OIL ON HIS LAND.

1169
01:03:45,821 --> 01:03:47,623
HIS LAND?

1170
01:03:47,623 --> 01:03:50,359
WELL, HERE WE GO.

1171
01:03:50,359 --> 01:03:52,695
NOW WE SEE IT ALL CLEAR AS DAY.

1172
01:03:52,695 --> 01:03:55,665
YOU STILL GOT THAT STUCK IN YOUR CRAW, DON’T YOU?

1173
01:03:55,665 --> 01:03:58,134
MY DADDY BOUGHT THAT LAND

1174
01:03:58,134 --> 01:04:01,637
FROM OLD SPARTA FAIR AND SQUARE.

1175
01:04:01,637 --> 01:04:03,339
AND HE STRUCK OIL ON IT A WEEK LATER.

1176
01:04:03,339 --> 01:04:05,875
DID IT EVER OCCUR TO YOU THAT MAYBE YOUR PA

1177
01:04:05,875 --> 01:04:08,244
WAS SO HELL-BENT ON WASTING HIS LIFE

1178
01:04:08,244 --> 01:04:11,314
WITH A STUPID DREAM OF A-- A CAMEL DYNASTY

1179
01:04:11,314 --> 01:04:15,718
THAT MY DADDY WAS FORCED TO GO OFF ON HIS OWN?!

1180
01:04:15,718 --> 01:04:17,320
NOW, MY DADDY TRIED FOR YEARS

1181
01:04:17,320 --> 01:04:19,822
TO GET OLD SPARTA TO DRILL FOR OIL,

1182
01:04:19,822 --> 01:04:23,292
BUT SPARTA WAS TOO DAMN STUBBORN.

1183
01:04:23,292 --> 01:04:26,996
THAT WASN’T THE WAY IT GOT TOLD TO ME.

1184
01:04:26,996 --> 01:04:28,931
BESIDES, THAT WASN’T THE POINT.

1185
01:04:28,931 --> 01:04:30,600
I WAS JUST COMPARING OUR UPBRINGINGS.

1186
01:04:30,600 --> 01:04:33,102
NO, YOU WEREN’T. NO, YOU WEREN’T.

1187
01:04:33,102 --> 01:04:35,238
GOD DAMN IT, YOU WERE CALLIN’ ME A SISSY.

1188
01:04:35,238 --> 01:04:36,606
THAT’S WHAT YOU WERE DOIN’.

1189
01:04:36,606 --> 01:04:38,908
THE HELL I WAS! THE HELL YOU WEREN’T!

1190
01:04:38,908 --> 01:04:40,610
MAYBE I DON’T KNOW HOW TO RIDE A HORSE.

1191
01:04:40,610 --> 01:04:42,345
MAYBE I’VE NEVER BEEN IN A REAL FIGHT,

1192
01:04:42,345 --> 01:04:44,947
BUT THAT DON’T MAKE ME LESS OF A MAN THAN YOU, ZACH WHIT!

1193
01:04:44,947 --> 01:04:47,016
YOU AIN’T NEVER BEEN IN A REAL FIGHT?

1194
01:04:48,551 --> 01:04:52,755
BY JESUS, BUT I TELL YOU WHAT.

1195
01:04:52,755 --> 01:04:55,891
I TELL YOU WHAT, ZACH--

1196
01:04:55,891 --> 01:04:58,261
I’M SORELY TEMPTED RIGHT NOW.

1197
01:04:58,261 --> 01:04:59,829
OH, NOW, EASY, NOW, CLINTON.

1198
01:04:59,829 --> 01:05:01,230
JUST SETTLE DOWN HERE.

1199
01:05:01,230 --> 01:05:02,632
COME ON, I’M GONNA PROVE IT TO YOU.

1200
01:05:02,632 --> 01:05:04,033
WHAT?

1201
01:05:04,033 --> 01:05:06,402
COME ON, I’M GONNA SHOW YOU WHAT I GOT.

1202
01:05:06,402 --> 01:05:07,903
COME ON.

1203
01:05:09,472 --> 01:05:12,108
LET’S PLAY TOE TICKLER.

1204
01:05:12,108 --> 01:05:13,843
TOE TICKLER? YEAH, THAT’S RIGHT.

1205
01:05:13,843 --> 01:05:15,244
CLINTON, WE’RE GROWN MEN HERE.

1206
01:05:15,244 --> 01:05:17,780
NOW, WHY DON’T WE BOTH JUST CALM DOWN

1207
01:05:17,780 --> 01:05:20,716
AND FINISH BUILDING THIS COFFIN FOR ROBERT E.?

1208
01:05:31,827 --> 01:05:34,764
WELL, I KNEW YOU WAS TOO YELLOW TO DO IT.

1209
01:05:42,104 --> 01:05:44,674
ALL RIGHT.

1210
01:05:46,842 --> 01:05:48,511
LET’S TICKLE THEM TOES.

1211
01:05:55,084 --> 01:05:56,986
[owl hooting]

1212
01:05:56,986 --> 01:05:59,588
(Walter) SO THIS IS WHERE THE WHITS END UP, HUH?

1213
01:05:59,588 --> 01:06:01,657
(Miranda) NOT ALL OF THEM.

1214
01:06:01,657 --> 01:06:06,195
THERE SHOULD BE ONE MORE,

1215
01:06:06,195 --> 01:06:09,131
ONE MORE SMALL GRAVE...

1216
01:06:12,068 --> 01:06:13,602
FOR MY BABY.

1217
01:06:15,338 --> 01:06:17,139
YOUR BABY?

1218
01:06:17,139 --> 01:06:19,075
WELL, IT WASN’T A REAL BABY.

1219
01:06:19,075 --> 01:06:21,177
IT WAS KIND OF A BABY-TO-BE.

1220
01:06:23,145 --> 01:06:25,514
YOU SEE, HIS FATHER WAS A CHEROKEE BRAVE,

1221
01:06:25,514 --> 01:06:28,517
AND DADDY JUST WOULDN’T LET ME MARRY HIM.

1222
01:06:28,517 --> 01:06:31,620
HE WOULDN’T HAVE NO HALF-BREED GRANDCHILD OUT OF WEDLOCK,

1223
01:06:31,620 --> 01:06:35,091
SO I WENT AND GAVE MYSELF AN ABORTION.

1224
01:06:39,595 --> 01:06:43,165
FUNNY, I THOUGHT THAT WOULD MAKE DADDY HAPPY,

1225
01:06:43,165 --> 01:06:47,970
BUT AFTER THAT, HE JUST KIND OF FROZE UP ON ME.

1226
01:06:51,273 --> 01:06:53,275
HE PLANTED THAT TREE IN THE BACKYARD

1227
01:06:53,275 --> 01:06:55,444
IN THE BABY’S MEMORY.

1228
01:06:57,046 --> 01:06:58,781
NOT LONG AFTER THAT--

1229
01:06:58,781 --> 01:07:00,716
I COULDN’T TELL YOU HOW LONG--

1230
01:07:00,716 --> 01:07:03,152
I FOUND MYSELF IN THE SANITARIUM.

1231
01:07:06,055 --> 01:07:07,957
JUST WHEN I THINK I’M GETTING BETTER,

1232
01:07:07,957 --> 01:07:12,261
I GO HOME, I SEE THAT TREE,

1233
01:07:12,261 --> 01:07:15,197
AND SUDDENLY, I’M SINKING TO THE BOTTOM OF THE OCEAN AGAIN.

1234
01:07:17,166 --> 01:07:18,534
[sighs]

1235
01:07:18,534 --> 01:07:21,437
SOUNDS TO ME LIKE THAT TREE GOT A HAINT ON IT.

1236
01:07:21,437 --> 01:07:23,639
[scoffs]

1237
01:07:23,639 --> 01:07:26,776
IF I WERE YOU, I’D...

1238
01:07:26,776 --> 01:07:29,278
I’D CUT THE DANG THING DOWN.

1239
01:07:44,760 --> 01:07:47,696
LESS THAN THIS IF YOU WANT TO WIN.

1240
01:08:00,209 --> 01:08:02,144
[thumps]

1241
01:08:07,616 --> 01:08:09,185
WELL, YOU’RE LUCKY.

1242
01:08:09,185 --> 01:08:13,889
IT’S JUST A PIECE OF YOUR TOE, NO STITCHES.

1243
01:08:13,889 --> 01:08:17,293
I’LL SEE IF I CAN’T DIG UP A FIRST AID KIT.

1244
01:08:17,293 --> 01:08:19,862
TRUNK OF MY CADDY. HERE ARE THE KEYS.

1245
01:08:19,862 --> 01:08:22,865
ALL RIGHT, BE BACK IN NO TIME.

1246
01:08:50,626 --> 01:08:52,695
YOU WANT TO EXPLAIN THIS, CLINTON?

1247
01:08:55,431 --> 01:08:58,367
(Clinton) THIS IS MY HOME.

1248
01:09:00,870 --> 01:09:04,540
WELL, THIS IS WHERE CHARLOTTE AND I LIVE.

1249
01:09:04,540 --> 01:09:06,375
I GOT NOTHING.

1250
01:09:08,544 --> 01:09:10,980
WELL, WHAT ABOUT THEM OIL RIGS OUT THERE?

1251
01:09:13,249 --> 01:09:15,384
YOU EVER SEE THEM PUMPING?

1252
01:09:17,520 --> 01:09:20,022
THE DAMN THINGS DRIED UP ON ME.

1253
01:09:20,022 --> 01:09:22,791
I JUST CAN’T BELIEVE THIS, CLINTON.

1254
01:09:22,791 --> 01:09:24,093
[laughs]

1255
01:09:24,093 --> 01:09:26,328
I HAVE A HARD TIME BELIEVING IT MYSELF.

1256
01:09:28,330 --> 01:09:31,867
NO SAVINGS?

1257
01:09:31,867 --> 01:09:33,869
STOCK MARKET.

1258
01:09:33,869 --> 01:09:35,804
LOST EVERYTHING TRYING TO WIN IT BACK.

1259
01:09:38,908 --> 01:09:40,576
YOU GOT ENOUGH TO LIVE?

1260
01:09:40,576 --> 01:09:42,111
YEAH, WELL,

1261
01:09:42,111 --> 01:09:45,147
NOT COUNTING WHAT I LOST TO YOU SHOOTING,

1262
01:09:45,147 --> 01:09:49,985
I GOT PROBABLY A WEEK TILL TUESDAY.

1263
01:09:49,985 --> 01:09:52,221
WE WERE HOPING OLD SPARTA WOULD, YOU KNOW,

1264
01:09:52,221 --> 01:09:54,223
LEAVE US SOMETHING IN HIS WILL, BUT, YOU KNOW,

1265
01:09:54,223 --> 01:09:57,059
IT JUST WASN’T MEANT TO BE, SO...

1266
01:09:57,059 --> 01:10:00,029
AT LEAST YOU DON’T HAVE ANY KIDS TO FEED.

1267
01:10:01,864 --> 01:10:06,502
YEAH, I GUESS WE CAN BE THANKFUL FOR THAT.

1268
01:10:11,941 --> 01:10:14,577
I AIN’T GONNA TELL ANYBODY ABOUT THIS, CLINTON,

1269
01:10:14,577 --> 01:10:16,845
NOT EVEN MARY JOAN.

1270
01:10:16,845 --> 01:10:19,448
WELL, I APPRECIATE THAT, ZACH.

1271
01:10:22,351 --> 01:10:26,288
WELL, LET’S WRAP THAT UP AND FINISH THAT COFFIN,

1272
01:10:26,288 --> 01:10:29,058
MR. TOE-TICKLING CHAMPION.

1273
01:11:27,750 --> 01:11:29,385
COME ON, GIMPY.

1274
01:11:29,385 --> 01:11:31,620
IF WE GET DRUNK NOW, WE CAN STILL BE SOBER

1275
01:11:31,620 --> 01:11:34,089
IN TIME TO TAKE CARE OF ROBERT E.

1276
01:11:34,089 --> 01:11:36,158
[laughs]

1277
01:11:42,631 --> 01:11:45,567
[saw scraping]

1278
01:12:07,256 --> 01:12:09,825
HEY, DON’T YOU THINK 6:00 IN THE MORNING

1279
01:12:09,825 --> 01:12:11,794
IS A LITTLE EARLY FOR PRUNING?

1280
01:12:13,662 --> 01:12:15,798
YOU KNOW, CUTTING IT DOWN IS NOT GONNA CHANGE ANYTHING.

1281
01:12:18,300 --> 01:12:20,335
YOU MEAN, IT WON’T CHANGE ANYTHING FOR YOU,

1282
01:12:20,335 --> 01:12:23,439
BUT FOR ME, IT’S GONNA DO A WORLD OF GOOD.

1283
01:12:26,008 --> 01:12:27,943
JUST OUT OF CURIOSITY, MARY JOAN,

1284
01:12:27,943 --> 01:12:30,346
WHEN ARE YOU GONNA FORGIVE ME?

1285
01:12:30,346 --> 01:12:33,382
I CAN’T FORGIVE YOU. ONLY GOD CAN DO THAT.

1286
01:12:33,382 --> 01:12:35,284
I’M NOT TALKING ABOUT THE BABY.

1287
01:12:35,284 --> 01:12:37,119
I WANT TO KNOW WHEN YOU’RE GONNA FORGIVE ME

1288
01:12:37,119 --> 01:12:39,021
FOR MY REAL SIN.

1289
01:12:39,021 --> 01:12:40,789
YOU’RE NOT MAKING ANY SENSE.

1290
01:12:40,789 --> 01:12:43,225
NOW, COME ON IN THE HOUSE AND GET SOME SLEEP.

1291
01:12:43,225 --> 01:12:46,662
YOU’VE ALWAYS HATED ME, LONG BEFORE THE ABORTION.

1292
01:12:46,662 --> 01:12:48,697
DON’T WASTE OUR TIME DENYING IT.

1293
01:12:48,697 --> 01:12:50,766
ALL RIGHT, YOU’RE NOT MY TYPE.

1294
01:12:50,766 --> 01:12:53,402
AND WHY IS IT, EXACTLY, YOU THINK THAT IS,

1295
01:12:53,402 --> 01:12:55,471
THAT YOU DON’T LIKE ME?

1296
01:12:55,471 --> 01:12:56,972
MIRANDA, I DON’T KNOW.

1297
01:12:56,972 --> 01:12:59,141
IT’S NOT SOMETHING CONCRETE

1298
01:12:59,141 --> 01:13:00,676
THAT I CAN PUT MY FINGER ON RIGHT NOW.

1299
01:13:00,676 --> 01:13:02,378
’CAUSE I WAS SO PRETTY.

1300
01:13:02,378 --> 01:13:05,447
THAT’S MY SIN, AND THAT MADE YOU JEALOUS,

1301
01:13:05,447 --> 01:13:08,450
’CAUSE ALL YOUR LIFE, YOU PLAYED BY THE RULES,

1302
01:13:08,450 --> 01:13:10,219
BUT ON A HOT SUMMER NIGHT,

1303
01:13:10,219 --> 01:13:13,455
THE BOYS DIDN’T EXACTLY GO LOOKING FOR NICE GIRLS.

1304
01:13:13,455 --> 01:13:15,257
WELL, MARY JOAN,

1305
01:13:15,257 --> 01:13:19,294
MAYBE IT SEEMS TO YOU THAT I HAVE DANCED WITH THE SERPENT,

1306
01:13:19,294 --> 01:13:23,132
THAT I HAVE OFFENDED THE MORAL CODE AND SANCTITY

1307
01:13:23,132 --> 01:13:25,634
OF THIS GODFORSAKEN STRETCH OF PRAIRIE,

1308
01:13:25,634 --> 01:13:27,336
BUT I HAVE PAID A VERY HIGH PRICE

1309
01:13:27,336 --> 01:13:30,239
FOR WHATEVER I’M SUPPOSED TO HAVE DONE TO Y’ALL,

1310
01:13:30,239 --> 01:13:31,840
AND MAYBE THAT AIN’T GOOD ENOUGH FOR YOU.

1311
01:13:31,840 --> 01:13:35,744
MAYBE YOU WANT ME TO TAKE MY LIFE

1312
01:13:35,744 --> 01:13:39,448
TO ATONE FOR TAKING THAT INDIAN BOY’S SEED.

1313
01:13:39,448 --> 01:13:41,817
WELL, I’LL LOOK YOU STRAIGHT IN THE EYE,

1314
01:13:41,817 --> 01:13:44,553
AND I’LL TELL YOU I WILL NOT SPEND THE REST OF MY LIFE

1315
01:13:44,553 --> 01:13:46,889
ROTTING AWAY IN THAT ASYLUM,

1316
01:13:46,889 --> 01:13:48,857
WAITING FOR YOUR FORGIVENESS.

1317
01:13:48,857 --> 01:13:51,794
SO THAT TREE IS COMING DOWN,

1318
01:13:51,794 --> 01:13:54,096
AND I’M GONNA PULL OUT ANYTHING BAD

1319
01:13:54,096 --> 01:13:56,131
THAT’S GROWN IN MY HEART

1320
01:13:56,131 --> 01:13:59,067
UNTIL I’M ABLE TO COME OUT AND START LIVING AGAIN.

1321
01:14:00,936 --> 01:14:02,437
YOU GIVE ME THAT SAW.

1322
01:14:02,437 --> 01:14:04,306
I DON’T THINK SO.

1323
01:14:04,306 --> 01:14:05,707
I SAID GIVE IT TO ME-- YOU GIVE--

1324
01:14:05,707 --> 01:14:07,509
OH!

1325
01:14:07,509 --> 01:14:10,579
I ONLY GIVE THINGS UP TO BOYS, MARY JOAN, DON’T YOU KNOW?

1326
01:14:10,579 --> 01:14:13,115
YOU WANT IT? YOU TAKE IT, OKAY, HONEY?

1327
01:14:13,115 --> 01:14:14,683
THESE ARE MY NEW SLIPPERS.

1328
01:14:14,683 --> 01:14:18,053
NOW, YOU GO AHEAD AND GIVE IT TO ME.

1329
01:14:18,053 --> 01:14:20,255
YOU’RE BEHAVING LIKE A CHILD, AND YOU’RE GONNA GET HURT.

1330
01:14:20,255 --> 01:14:22,257
YES, I AM.

1331
01:14:22,257 --> 01:14:25,460
MIRANDA, GIVE ME THE SAW.

1332
01:14:25,460 --> 01:14:27,362
I’M LIKE ONE OF THOSE SAVAGES YOU SEE

1333
01:14:27,362 --> 01:14:28,797
IN THE NATIONAL GEOGRAPHIC.

1334
01:14:28,797 --> 01:14:30,699
YOU WANT TO COMMUNICATE WITH ME?

1335
01:14:30,699 --> 01:14:33,635
THEN YOU’VE GOT TO DESCEND TO MY PRIMITIVE,

1336
01:14:33,635 --> 01:14:36,638
CARNAL, SINFUL LEVEL.

1337
01:14:36,638 --> 01:14:37,673
UHH!

1338
01:14:43,145 --> 01:14:44,079
AAH!

1339
01:14:47,416 --> 01:14:50,352
[both screaming]

1340
01:14:53,288 --> 01:14:55,057
OH, LORD.

1341
01:14:59,161 --> 01:15:01,496
MIRANDA, MARY JOAN!

1342
01:15:03,165 --> 01:15:05,033
OHH! [gasps]

1343
01:15:06,368 --> 01:15:08,670
[grunting]

1344
01:15:12,641 --> 01:15:14,509
[laughs]

1345
01:15:14,509 --> 01:15:16,144
[laughter]

1346
01:15:24,553 --> 01:15:27,556
[sobbing]

1347
01:15:31,960 --> 01:15:34,062
(Mary Joan) MIRANDA, WHAT IS IT?

1348
01:15:34,062 --> 01:15:36,531
I DIDN’T HAVE ANY ABORTION.

1349
01:15:38,400 --> 01:15:40,903
BUT I ABORTED MY BABY...

1350
01:15:45,107 --> 01:15:47,109
IN HERE.

1351
01:15:49,011 --> 01:15:51,813
IN HERE, I ABORTED MY BABY.

1352
01:15:51,813 --> 01:15:54,449
I PLANNED ON GOING TO THE CITY AND HAVING IT DONE,

1353
01:15:54,449 --> 01:15:57,386
ONLY GOD BEAT ME TO IT.

1354
01:16:01,356 --> 01:16:05,227
IT JUST FLOWED OUT OF ME.

1355
01:16:07,229 --> 01:16:11,767
PART OF ME DIED,

1356
01:16:11,767 --> 01:16:14,269
AND IT HURT.

1357
01:16:14,269 --> 01:16:18,307
IT HURT LIKE I’VE NEVER, EVER BEEN HURT.

1358
01:16:20,409 --> 01:16:22,244
MIRANDA, WHY WOULD YOU SAY

1359
01:16:22,244 --> 01:16:26,515
THAT YOU HAD AN ABORTION WHEN YOU HAD A MISCARRIAGE?

1360
01:16:26,515 --> 01:16:29,418
BECAUSE I DIDN’T.

1361
01:16:29,418 --> 01:16:33,488
IN MY HEART, I KILLED MY BABY.

1362
01:16:34,890 --> 01:16:37,859
THAT’S WHY GOD TOOK HIM.

1363
01:16:37,859 --> 01:16:39,928
WE CAN’T LIE TO GOD.

1364
01:16:39,928 --> 01:16:41,630
YOU WOULDN’T UNDERSTAND, MARY JOAN.

1365
01:16:41,630 --> 01:16:43,799
YOU JUST WOULDN’T UNDERSTAND.

1366
01:16:47,336 --> 01:16:50,639
I TRIED TO HOLD IT.

1367
01:16:50,639 --> 01:16:53,675
I JUST KEPT WONDERING IF GOD WAS PUNISHING ME,

1368
01:16:53,675 --> 01:16:56,611
PUNISHING ME FOR LOVING THAT BOY,

1369
01:16:56,611 --> 01:16:59,481
FOR GIVING HIM ALL THE LOVE I HAD.

1370
01:16:59,481 --> 01:17:03,952
HE’S NOT PUNISHING YOU, MIRANDA.

1371
01:17:03,952 --> 01:17:07,255
AND IF HE IS, WELL...

1372
01:17:07,255 --> 01:17:10,425
THEN HE’S AN ASSHOLE.

1373
01:17:10,425 --> 01:17:14,196
OH, LORD. AM I GONNA GO TO HELL FOR SAYING THAT?

1374
01:17:14,196 --> 01:17:17,165
ONLY IF GOD REALLY IS AN ASSHOLE, HONEY.

1375
01:17:17,165 --> 01:17:23,572
[laughter]

1376
01:17:23,572 --> 01:17:27,242
COME ON. 12?

1377
01:17:27,242 --> 01:17:29,244
12, MY BUTT.

1378
01:17:29,244 --> 01:17:31,513
SWEAR TO GOD.

1379
01:17:31,513 --> 01:17:32,914
MY BUTT.

1380
01:17:32,914 --> 01:17:35,917
SWEAR TO GOD.

1381
01:17:35,917 --> 01:17:37,819
GOD. WELL...

1382
01:17:37,819 --> 01:17:39,988
I DIDN’T DO IT UNTIL I WAS 16.

1383
01:17:39,988 --> 01:17:41,623
I’M SORRY FOR YOU.

1384
01:17:41,623 --> 01:17:44,559
[both laugh]

1385
01:17:44,559 --> 01:17:45,794
WHO WITH?

1386
01:17:47,929 --> 01:17:49,331
JENNY.

1387
01:17:49,331 --> 01:17:51,833
THE MAID? YES, SIR.

1388
01:17:51,833 --> 01:17:53,802
WHEW.

1389
01:17:53,802 --> 01:17:57,172
YES, SIR, AND SHE WAS SWEET AS PEACH PIE.

1390
01:17:57,172 --> 01:17:59,474
[both laughing]

1391
01:18:02,144 --> 01:18:03,912
THERE I WAS.

1392
01:18:03,912 --> 01:18:08,683
I WAS ORGANIZING MY SHOE TREE,

1393
01:18:08,683 --> 01:18:13,355
AND THEN I--I FELT THIS BIG OLD WET LIP

1394
01:18:13,355 --> 01:18:15,057
RIGHT ON MY EAR.

1395
01:18:15,057 --> 01:18:16,725
AHH.

1396
01:18:16,725 --> 01:18:19,695
AND BOOM, BANG-- I WAS A MAN.

1397
01:18:19,695 --> 01:18:22,330
[both laughing]

1398
01:18:22,330 --> 01:18:24,533
THAT MUST’VE BEEN GREAT.

1399
01:18:24,533 --> 01:18:27,402
HELL NO. I WAS SCARED TO DEATH.

1400
01:18:27,402 --> 01:18:30,138
AND THEN WHEN MY MAN-ROOT GOT SWOLLEN.

1401
01:18:30,138 --> 01:18:33,041
[both laughing]

1402
01:18:33,041 --> 01:18:35,043
I THOUGHT I HAD TETANUS!

1403
01:18:35,043 --> 01:18:36,611
[laughter]

1404
01:18:36,611 --> 01:18:38,246
I DIDN’T KNOW WHAT WAS GOIN’ ON.

1405
01:18:38,246 --> 01:18:40,015
SHE WENT FOR THE EAR, HUH?

1406
01:18:40,015 --> 01:18:43,085
IT’S THE DAMNEDEST THING.

1407
01:18:43,085 --> 01:18:44,453
YOU KNOW WHAT?

1408
01:18:44,453 --> 01:18:46,054
I’M GONNA TELL YOU SOMETHING NOW

1409
01:18:46,054 --> 01:18:47,456
IN THE STRICTEST OF CONFIDENCES.

1410
01:18:47,456 --> 01:18:50,992
OH, OF COURSE. CHARLOTTE IS THE EXACT SAME WAY.

1411
01:18:50,992 --> 01:18:52,594
SHE’LL GO RIGHT FOR MY EAR.

1412
01:18:52,594 --> 01:18:54,029
IT’S THE GOD DAMNEDEST THING.

1413
01:18:54,029 --> 01:18:56,198
OH, I’M NOT SURPRISED. MARY JOAN, TOO.

1414
01:18:56,198 --> 01:18:58,667
YOU KNOW WHAT IT IS, DON’T YOU? NO.

1415
01:18:58,667 --> 01:19:00,902
DIDN’T YOUR DADDY TELL YOU?

1416
01:19:00,902 --> 01:19:03,071
WELL, I GUESS HE DIED TOO SOON.

1417
01:19:03,071 --> 01:19:05,907
WELL, I DIDN’T FIND OUT ABOUT IT MYSELF

1418
01:19:05,907 --> 01:19:09,211
UNTIL I WAS ABOUT READY TO GO OFF TO BOOT CAMP.

1419
01:19:09,211 --> 01:19:11,980
YOU ARE TRULY A MAN NOW, ZACH,

1420
01:19:11,980 --> 01:19:14,616
SO IT’S TIME YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT THE AWESOME POWER

1421
01:19:14,616 --> 01:19:17,185
OF THE MALE WHIT’S EAR.

1422
01:19:17,185 --> 01:19:20,222
SOME CALL IT A BLESSING, SOME CALL IT A CURSE,

1423
01:19:20,222 --> 01:19:22,524
BUT THEY ALL AGREE ON ONE THING.

1424
01:19:22,524 --> 01:19:24,593
THERE IS SOMETHING TRULY MYSTICAL

1425
01:19:24,593 --> 01:19:26,862
ABOUT THE EARS OF THE WHIT MENFOLK

1426
01:19:26,862 --> 01:19:30,532
THAT TURNS WOMEN INTO WILD, LUSTFUL CREATURES

1427
01:19:30,532 --> 01:19:32,601
WITH NO OTHER THOUGHT THAN THE SATISFACTION

1428
01:19:32,601 --> 01:19:35,437
OF THEIR ANIMAL URGES.

1429
01:19:35,437 --> 01:19:37,005
NO KIDDING?

1430
01:19:37,005 --> 01:19:40,142
TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH, I DIDN’T BELIEVE IT 100% UNTIL NOW.

1431
01:19:40,142 --> 01:19:41,576
THE EAR, HUH?

1432
01:19:41,576 --> 01:19:43,111
YEAH.

1433
01:19:43,111 --> 01:19:45,113
IT’S NO WONDER MY DADDY WORE A HAT.

1434
01:19:45,113 --> 01:19:46,481
GOD DAMN.

1435
01:19:46,481 --> 01:19:48,150
(Miranda) NOW, PULL!

1436
01:19:48,150 --> 01:19:49,851
CHARLOTTE, PULL!

1437
01:19:49,851 --> 01:19:51,186
WHAT IN THE HELL IS THAT?

1438
01:19:51,186 --> 01:19:52,988
LEAN INTO IT.

1439
01:19:52,988 --> 01:19:56,324
[all screaming]

1440
01:19:56,324 --> 01:19:57,659
[all cheering]

1441
01:19:57,659 --> 01:20:00,262
(Miranda) WE GOT IT.

1442
01:20:00,262 --> 01:20:01,596
MORNIN’.

1443
01:20:03,431 --> 01:20:04,933
Y’ALL DOING SOME GARDENING?

1444
01:20:04,933 --> 01:20:08,103
OH, JUST CLEARING OUT A LITTLE DEAD WOOD.

1445
01:20:10,071 --> 01:20:11,907
A MAN SPENDS THE FIRST HALF OF HIS LIFE

1446
01:20:11,907 --> 01:20:13,542
TRYING TO UNDERSTAND WOMEN

1447
01:20:13,542 --> 01:20:16,077
AND THE SECOND HALF TRYING TO FORGET WHAT HE’S LEARNED.

1448
01:20:16,077 --> 01:20:17,312
(Clinton) UH-HUH.

1449
01:20:17,312 --> 01:20:19,147
WOMEN.

1450
01:20:20,849 --> 01:20:23,785
[camel lowing]

1451
01:20:28,390 --> 01:20:30,158
HE’S IN PAIN, SON.

1452
01:20:30,158 --> 01:20:31,893
HE’S IN PAIN,

1453
01:20:31,893 --> 01:20:33,795
AND HE WANTS TO DIE.

1454
01:20:33,795 --> 01:20:37,499
(Jefferson) YOU’D LIKE TO HELP HIM, WOULDN’T YOU?

1455
01:20:37,499 --> 01:20:39,534
WELL, THERE’S ONLY ONE WAY YOU CAN.

1456
01:20:39,534 --> 01:20:41,803
YOU KNOW WHAT THAT IS, DON’T YOU?

1457
01:20:41,803 --> 01:20:43,438
LOOK AT ROBERT E.

1458
01:20:43,438 --> 01:20:45,073
[groans]

1459
01:20:45,073 --> 01:20:47,375
THE ANSWER IS IN HIS EYES.

1460
01:20:49,244 --> 01:20:51,146
♪

1461
01:21:37,459 --> 01:21:39,894
[gunshot]

1462
01:22:17,932 --> 01:22:21,970
OH, HONEY, GET A LITTLE SLEEP BEFORE THE FUNERAL.

1463
01:22:21,970 --> 01:22:23,638
WHAT IS IT?

1464
01:22:25,106 --> 01:22:26,941
ZACH.

1465
01:22:26,941 --> 01:22:30,512
IT SEEMS LIKE WE TELL A LOT OF WHITE LIES IN THIS FAMILY.

1466
01:22:32,280 --> 01:22:34,749
ONLY THING-- A WHITE LIE CAN TURN MIGHTY BLACK

1467
01:22:34,749 --> 01:22:37,085
IF IT SITS IN SOMEONE’S HEAD LONG ENOUGH.

1468
01:22:37,085 --> 01:22:39,854
HONEY, WHAT BROUGHT ALL THIS UP?

1469
01:22:42,123 --> 01:22:44,693
MARY JOAN,

1470
01:22:44,693 --> 01:22:47,829
YOU THINK I’M FIT TO RUN THIS FAMILY?

1471
01:22:47,829 --> 01:22:50,098
BECAUSE IT’S ALL ON ME NOW THAT DADDY’S GONE,

1472
01:22:50,098 --> 01:22:53,001
AND I WANT TO KNOW WHAT YOU THINK.

1473
01:22:55,236 --> 01:22:59,741
I THINK THIS FAMILY IS LUCKY

1474
01:22:59,741 --> 01:23:01,977
TO HAVE A MAN OF YOUR CHARACTER LOOKING OVER US.

1475
01:23:01,977 --> 01:23:03,712
NOW, WHY WOULD YOU ASK ME A THING LIKE THAT?

1476
01:23:07,816 --> 01:23:09,451
SOMETIMES...

1477
01:23:11,953 --> 01:23:15,924
I GET THE FEELING YOU DON’T THINK TOO MUCH OF ME.

1478
01:23:18,493 --> 01:23:21,296
DON’T GET ME WRONG.

1479
01:23:21,296 --> 01:23:23,031
I THINK THAT YOU LOVE ME AND ALL.

1480
01:23:23,031 --> 01:23:26,534
IT’S JUST THAT SOMETIMES I THINK YOU FIGURED

1481
01:23:26,534 --> 01:23:29,804
YOU MARRIED BENEATH YOURSELF, AND YOU DID.

1482
01:23:31,473 --> 01:23:35,877
LOOK AT YOU. YOU’RE SO PRETTY.

1483
01:23:35,877 --> 01:23:37,612
[laughs]

1484
01:23:37,612 --> 01:23:40,515
YOU GOT A COLLEGE EDUCATION.

1485
01:23:40,515 --> 01:23:44,619
YOU COULD HAVE DONE BETTER, AND THAT’S THE TRUTH.

1486
01:23:44,619 --> 01:23:47,455
HONEY, I MARRIED YOU, BECAUSE I SAW A GENUINE HERO,

1487
01:23:47,455 --> 01:23:49,124
AND I STILL SEE ONE.

1488
01:23:49,124 --> 01:23:50,892
NOW, HOW LONG HAVE YOU BEEN THINKING

1489
01:23:50,892 --> 01:23:53,161
ABOUT ALL THIS NONSENSE?

1490
01:23:55,897 --> 01:23:58,833
MOSTLY SINCE DADDY’S GONE.

1491
01:24:02,604 --> 01:24:05,940
ZACH, DID I DO SOMETHING TO MAKE YOU FEEL THIS WAY?

1492
01:24:11,980 --> 01:24:13,815
IF WE STAY IN TEXAS...

1493
01:24:15,683 --> 01:24:18,620
WE’RE ALWAYS GONNA DRIVE AN OLD CAR,

1494
01:24:18,620 --> 01:24:21,890
AND YOU’LL BE BUYING YOUR DRESSES IN THE BASEMENT OF SOME THRIFT STORE,

1495
01:24:21,890 --> 01:24:24,959
AND MAYBE IF LITTLE SPARTA DOES START TALKING AGAIN,

1496
01:24:24,959 --> 01:24:26,795
I AIN’T GONNA BE ABLE TO SEND HIM TO COLLEGE.

1497
01:24:26,795 --> 01:24:28,863
HONEY, WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

1498
01:24:35,770 --> 01:24:37,405
[sighs]

1499
01:24:39,174 --> 01:24:41,643
I’M GONNA TAKE THAT JOB UP NORTH.

1500
01:24:41,643 --> 01:24:45,146
WE’RE GONNA MOVE TO NEW YORK.

1501
01:24:48,817 --> 01:24:51,286
WELL, HONEY, YOU KNOW WHATEVER DECISIONS YOU HAVE TO MAKE,

1502
01:24:51,286 --> 01:24:53,788
I’M GONNA STAND BEHIND YOU 100%.

1503
01:24:53,788 --> 01:24:56,658
REALLY? REALLY, HONEY.

1504
01:24:56,658 --> 01:24:58,426
[laughs]

1505
01:25:06,901 --> 01:25:10,538
(Zach) LITTLE SPARTA, COULD YOU BE QUIET FOR A WHILE?

1506
01:25:10,538 --> 01:25:12,507
(Sparta) LITTLE SPARTA,

1507
01:25:12,507 --> 01:25:15,810
THIS HERE IS YOUR GREAT-GREAT-GREAT- GRANDDADDY, LUCAS.

1508
01:25:15,810 --> 01:25:18,379
(Lucas) WHEN I SAW HANNIBAL STANDING THERE...

1509
01:25:18,379 --> 01:25:20,548
(Murtis) OLD ACHILLES WAS SPEAKER OF THE HOUSE IN AUSTIN,

1510
01:25:20,548 --> 01:25:22,617
AND EVERYBODY KNEW HE’D GO ON TO BE GOVERNOR.

1511
01:25:22,617 --> 01:25:25,587
(Sparta) THAT GUN SCARES YOU, DON’T IT?

1512
01:25:25,587 --> 01:25:28,389
(Murtis) FAMILY IS FAMILY, SPARTA.

1513
01:25:28,389 --> 01:25:29,958
(Sparta) LOOK AT ROBERT E.

1514
01:25:29,958 --> 01:25:32,961
THE ANSWER IS IN HIS EYES.

1515
01:25:32,961 --> 01:25:35,196
[gunshot]

1516
01:25:37,165 --> 01:25:39,467
HEY, WAKE UP, BOY.

1517
01:25:40,969 --> 01:25:42,971
♪

1518
01:26:12,433 --> 01:26:14,569
IT’S REAL SAD, I KNOW.

1519
01:26:14,569 --> 01:26:16,604
BUT I’M SO PROUD OF YOU

1520
01:26:16,604 --> 01:26:19,474
FOR DOING THE RIGHT THING BY ROBERT E.

1521
01:26:19,474 --> 01:26:21,009
CLIMB UP, PARTNER.

1522
01:26:21,009 --> 01:26:22,944
LET’S GO FOR A RIDE.

1523
01:26:22,944 --> 01:26:24,546
ALL RIGHT.

1524
01:26:26,481 --> 01:26:28,349
OH, LOOK AT THAT, BOY.

1525
01:26:28,349 --> 01:26:30,451
THIS IS TEXAS.

1526
01:26:30,451 --> 01:26:33,821
THIS IS YOUR REAL INHERITANCE.

1527
01:26:35,256 --> 01:26:37,992
YOU KNOW WHY TEXAS IS SO DAMN HOT?

1528
01:26:37,992 --> 01:26:39,894
BECAUSE SO MANY WHIT MEN CAME HERE

1529
01:26:39,894 --> 01:26:41,930
AND RAISED SO MUCH HELL.

1530
01:26:41,930 --> 01:26:44,666
MAYBE THAT’S WHERE WE MADE A LITTLE MISTAKE, YOU SEE.

1531
01:26:44,666 --> 01:26:46,868
INSTEAD OF RAISING SO MUCH HELL ALL THE TIME,

1532
01:26:46,868 --> 01:26:48,703
WE SHOULD HAVE REACHED UP AND TRIED TO PULL DOWN

1533
01:26:48,703 --> 01:26:50,305
A LITTLE BIT OF HEAVEN EVERY NOW AND THEN.

1534
01:26:50,305 --> 01:26:52,473
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

1535
01:26:52,473 --> 01:26:54,309
[laughs] NO.

1536
01:26:54,309 --> 01:26:56,244
WELL, LET ME PUT IT THIS WAY.

1537
01:26:56,244 --> 01:26:59,747
LIFE IS AN ORNERY CAMEL, LITTLE SPARTA,

1538
01:26:59,747 --> 01:27:01,916
AND IT WILL DRAG YOUR SORRY ASS

1539
01:27:01,916 --> 01:27:04,452
THROUGH THE MOST GODFORSAKEN DESERTS ON EARTH.

1540
01:27:04,452 --> 01:27:07,222
THE TRICK IS TO HOLD ON TIGHT,

1541
01:27:07,222 --> 01:27:10,391
AND IF YOU DO THAT, THAT NASTY CRITTER

1542
01:27:10,391 --> 01:27:13,027
MIGHT JUST GIVE YOU THE RIDE OF YOUR LIFE.

1543
01:27:13,027 --> 01:27:17,065
WELL, THIS PART OF OUR JOURNEY IS COMING TO AN END TOGETHER.

1544
01:27:17,065 --> 01:27:19,500
THERE’S JUST ONE LAST THING.

1545
01:27:19,500 --> 01:27:21,035
LISTEN UP, NOW.

1546
01:27:21,035 --> 01:27:22,337
I WANT MY EAR BACK.

1547
01:27:22,337 --> 01:27:24,005
NOW, WAIT A MINUTE! DON’T GET SCARED.

1548
01:27:24,005 --> 01:27:26,174
IT’S MY EAR, DAMN IT, AND I WANT IT BACK.

1549
01:27:26,174 --> 01:27:27,642
IS IT A DEAL?

1550
01:27:27,642 --> 01:27:29,777
COME ON, PARTNER.

1551
01:27:29,777 --> 01:27:31,279
THAT’S MY BOY.

1552
01:27:31,279 --> 01:27:33,448
THANK YOU.

1553
01:27:33,448 --> 01:27:38,052
WELL, I’M ABOUT OUT OF SURPRISES, LITTLE SPARTA.

1554
01:27:38,052 --> 01:27:41,789
NOW, JUST REMEMBER, YOU’VE GOT A BURNING DROP

1555
01:27:41,789 --> 01:27:44,525
OF EVERY WHIT THAT’S EVER LIVED FLOWING IN YOUR VEINS,

1556
01:27:44,525 --> 01:27:46,928
AND YOU GOT FIRE IN YOUR HEART.

1557
01:27:46,928 --> 01:27:48,630
USE THAT FIRE

1558
01:27:48,630 --> 01:27:52,834
TO FORGE ONE HELL OF A WONDERFUL LIFE FOR YOURSELF,

1559
01:27:52,834 --> 01:27:55,003
AND EVERY NOW AND THEN, YOU JUST REMEMBER YOUR GRANDPA

1560
01:27:55,003 --> 01:27:57,105
WITH A LITTLE PRAYER,

1561
01:27:57,105 --> 01:27:58,740
AND I’LL BE RIGHT THERE WITH YOU.

1562
01:27:58,740 --> 01:28:01,142
HOW’D THAT BE?

1563
01:28:01,142 --> 01:28:03,745
LET ME GIVE YOU A KISS GOOD-BYE.

1564
01:28:05,813 --> 01:28:07,015
(Zach) SPARTA!

1565
01:28:07,015 --> 01:28:09,050
COME ON BACK, SON.

1566
01:28:09,050 --> 01:28:12,186
YOUR GRANDMAMA’S FIXING YOU BREAKFAST.

1567
01:28:32,140 --> 01:28:34,108
LET’S GO, MAMA!

1568
01:28:34,108 --> 01:28:36,077
DADDY’S ABOUT TO ARRIVE ANY SECOND.

1569
01:28:36,077 --> 01:28:38,346
ABOUT GAVE UP THE GHOST ON YOU TWO.

1570
01:28:38,346 --> 01:28:41,416
WELL, WE OVERSLEPT.

1571
01:28:41,416 --> 01:28:43,351
I’LL BE DARNED.

1572
01:28:45,219 --> 01:28:47,055
(woman) THANK YOU, DEAR.

1573
01:28:47,055 --> 01:28:49,290
[people speaking softly]

1574
01:28:55,163 --> 01:28:57,665
♪

1575
01:29:37,972 --> 01:29:40,908
[man speaking indistinctly]

1576
01:29:45,947 --> 01:29:47,949
[together] AMEN.

1577
01:30:19,380 --> 01:30:20,848
(Murtis) LITTLE SPARTA...

1578
01:30:20,848 --> 01:30:22,083
[gasps]

1579
01:30:22,083 --> 01:30:23,951
WAS THAT YOUR GRANDDADDY’S EAR?

1580
01:30:26,154 --> 01:30:29,557
WELL, IT’S BACK WHERE IT BELONGS...

1581
01:30:30,892 --> 01:30:32,660
THANK GOD.

1582
01:30:32,660 --> 01:30:35,596
DANG THING ABOUT DROVE ME CRAZY.

1583
01:30:42,103 --> 01:30:44,205
APPRECIATE YOU TAKING MIRANDA BACK.

1584
01:30:44,205 --> 01:30:46,174
IT’S MY PLEASURE.

1585
01:30:46,174 --> 01:30:48,376
WHERE IN HELL IS SHE?

1586
01:30:57,752 --> 01:31:00,154
TAKE GOOD CARE OF YOURSELF, MIRANDA.

1587
01:31:00,154 --> 01:31:03,157
YOU HEAR? LOOK ME UP WHEN YOU SURFACE.

1588
01:31:03,157 --> 01:31:05,593
I CERTAINLY WILL.

1589
01:31:26,247 --> 01:31:28,015
BEST OF LUCK TO Y’ALL.

1590
01:31:29,617 --> 01:31:31,552
HEY, CLINTON, YOU TAKE GOOD CARE OF THAT CADDY.

1591
01:31:31,552 --> 01:31:33,588
[laughs] OKAY, I WILL, WALTER.

1592
01:31:35,990 --> 01:31:37,458
ZACH.

1593
01:31:37,458 --> 01:31:40,995
BE GOOD, WALTER. WILL DO, WILL DO.

1594
01:31:40,995 --> 01:31:42,697
BYE!

1595
01:31:42,697 --> 01:31:44,365
BYE, Y’ALL. BYE, WALTER.

1596
01:31:48,135 --> 01:31:50,838
THAT NEGRO’S A PISTOL, AIN’T HE?

1597
01:31:50,838 --> 01:31:53,140
THAT NEGRO’S GONNA BE A DOCTOR.

1598
01:31:53,140 --> 01:31:55,309
SOMEDAY HE MAY SAVE YOUR LIFE.

1599
01:31:55,309 --> 01:31:59,413
YOU KNOW, THE WORLD’S A-CHANGING, AIN’T IT?

1600
01:31:59,413 --> 01:32:02,149
COME ON, CLINTON, I GOT SOMETHING FOR YOU.

1601
01:32:02,149 --> 01:32:04,719
NOW, YOU KNOW I LOVE YOU,

1602
01:32:04,719 --> 01:32:07,855
AND YOU KNOW I’LL BE THINKIN’ ABOUT YOU EVERY DAY.

1603
01:32:07,855 --> 01:32:10,658
[baby talk]

1604
01:32:10,658 --> 01:32:13,060
NOW, YOU TELL YOUR MAMA AND DADDY

1605
01:32:13,060 --> 01:32:15,897
TO COME VISIT ME HERE FOR CHRISTMAS.

1606
01:32:15,897 --> 01:32:18,266
’CAUSE IF I HAVE TO GO UP TO NEW YORK,

1607
01:32:18,266 --> 01:32:21,135
I’M JUST LIKELY TO FREEZE TO DEATH.

1608
01:32:24,906 --> 01:32:28,643
DON’T YOU THINK IT’S TIME YOU STARTED TALKIN’ AGAIN?

1609
01:32:30,244 --> 01:32:31,812
SEE YOU AROUND.

1610
01:32:35,449 --> 01:32:38,052
OH, YOU DON’T HAVE THIS KIND OF MONEY, ZACH.

1611
01:32:38,052 --> 01:32:42,089
WELL, THANKS TO THE INHERITANCE, I DO.

1612
01:32:42,089 --> 01:32:44,725
WELL, I’M-- I’M TRULY TOUCHED, BUT I--

1613
01:32:44,725 --> 01:32:48,596
HEY, CLINTON, OIL WELLS MAY DRY UP,

1614
01:32:48,596 --> 01:32:50,064
BUT BLOOD IS FOREVER.

1615
01:32:50,064 --> 01:32:53,401
NOW, DON’T ARGUE.

1616
01:32:53,401 --> 01:32:56,437
WELL, YOU JUST CAN’T GIVE THIS KIND OF MONEY AWAY.

1617
01:32:56,437 --> 01:32:59,440
WELL, I DIDN’T EXACTLY SAY I WAS GIVING IT TO YOU.

1618
01:32:59,440 --> 01:33:01,475
[laughs]

1619
01:33:01,475 --> 01:33:04,979
THERE’S, UH...

1620
01:33:04,979 --> 01:33:08,683
THERE’S SOMETHING I’D LIKE TO BUY FROM YOU.

1621
01:33:08,683 --> 01:33:10,084
BYE, MURTIS. (Charlotte) BYE-BYE.

1622
01:33:10,084 --> 01:33:12,253
(Zach) BYE, MAMA. I LOVE YOU.

1623
01:33:13,921 --> 01:33:16,090
♪

1624
01:33:24,966 --> 01:33:27,935
SUGARBUSH, I GOT SOME GOOD NEWS AND SOME BAD NEWS.

1625
01:33:27,935 --> 01:33:29,704
WHAT IS IT?

1626
01:33:29,704 --> 01:33:32,173
THE BAD NEWS IS, YOU’RE GONNA HAVE WAIT A WHILE FOR THAT CADILLAC.

1627
01:33:32,173 --> 01:33:35,876
HONEY, YOU KNOW I DON’T CARE ABOUT ANY OLD CADILLAC.

1628
01:33:35,876 --> 01:33:37,311
HEY.

1629
01:33:37,311 --> 01:33:38,913
HEY, HEY, HEY!

1630
01:33:38,913 --> 01:33:41,115
YOU GET YOUR LIPS OFF MY EAR RIGHT NOW!

1631
01:33:41,115 --> 01:33:43,718
WHAT’S GOT INTO YOU, WOMAN? [laughs]

1632
01:33:43,718 --> 01:33:45,720
YOU’RE JUST SO CUTE, I CAN’T HELP IT.

1633
01:33:45,720 --> 01:33:47,822
WELL, I HEARD THAT BEFORE.

1634
01:33:47,822 --> 01:33:49,490
OH! YOU DID? WHAT’S THE GOOD NEWS, HONEY?

1635
01:33:49,490 --> 01:33:50,958
THE GOOD NEWS IS, WE’RE GONNA HAVE

1636
01:33:50,958 --> 01:33:52,927
THAT FAMOUS WHIT BARBEQUE TONIGHT.

1637
01:33:52,927 --> 01:33:54,628
HELL, WE CAN HAVE IT ANY NIGHT WE WANT.

1638
01:33:54,628 --> 01:33:56,430
’CAUSE I MADE A DEAL WITH CLINTON.

1639
01:33:56,430 --> 01:33:58,799
"HELL"? IS "HELL" A WORD YOU WANT HIM REPEATING?

1640
01:33:58,799 --> 01:34:00,935
HE DON’T REPEAT ANYTHING! HE’S A LITTLE MUTE BOY. RIGHT, SPARTA?

1641
01:34:00,935 --> 01:34:02,637
THE HELL I AM!

1642
01:34:02,637 --> 01:34:05,072
HEY, YOU’RE TALKING AGAIN.

1643
01:34:05,072 --> 01:34:07,942
WELL, I’M GLAD TO SEE THAT’S OVER AND DONE WITH,

1644
01:34:07,942 --> 01:34:11,078
BUT DON’T YOU EVER LET ME HEAR YOU CURSING AGAIN, OR ELSE I’LL--

1645
01:34:11,078 --> 01:34:12,913
I’LL STOP IF YOU’LL STOP, DADDY.

1646
01:34:12,913 --> 01:34:15,149
WHAT?

1647
01:34:20,788 --> 01:34:23,357
WELL, ALL RIGHT,

1648
01:34:23,357 --> 01:34:25,826
BUT LET’S SHAKE ON THE DEAL.

1649
01:34:25,826 --> 01:34:28,195
WHOA. OH!

1650
01:34:28,195 --> 01:34:29,997
[laughs] LITTLE SPARTA.

1651
01:34:31,265 --> 01:34:33,567
[laughter]

1652
01:34:33,567 --> 01:34:35,903
(Zach) BOY, YOU ABOUT AS STUBBORN AS HECK.

1653
01:34:35,903 --> 01:34:38,039
YOU CAN THANK YOUR MOTHER’S SIDE OF THE FAMILY FOR THAT.

1654
01:34:38,039 --> 01:34:40,207
(Mary Joan) STUBBORN AS HECK? YOU’RE STUBBORN--

1655
01:34:40,207 --> 01:34:42,743
HEY, KEEP YOUR HANDS ON THE WHEEL.

1656
01:34:42,743 --> 01:34:44,478
(Zach) I GOT MY HANDS ON THE WHEEL.

1657
01:34:44,478 --> 01:34:46,147
LET ME DRIVE.

1658
01:34:47,882 --> 01:34:50,051
♪

1659
01:35:01,128 --> 01:35:02,730
THANK YOU, ROBERT E.

1660
01:35:02,730 --> 01:35:05,666
I SURE DIDN’T WANT TO MAKE THIS TRIP ALONE.

1661
01:35:08,035 --> 01:35:10,304
[camel chuffing]

1662
01:35:12,139 --> 01:35:15,076
[camel lowing]

1663
01:35:31,892 --> 01:35:33,961
[camel growling]

1664
01:35:37,898 --> 01:35:39,767
[Patsy Cline’s Walking Dream]

1665
01:35:42,369 --> 01:35:44,638
♪ A WALKIN’ DREAM ♪

1666
01:35:44,638 --> 01:35:48,142
♪ I DREAMED ABOUT YOU

1667
01:35:48,142 --> 01:35:50,578
♪ A WALKIN’ DREAM ♪

1668
01:35:50,578 --> 01:35:53,781
♪ CAN’T DO WITHOUT YOU ♪

1669
01:35:53,781 --> 01:35:56,016
♪ LOVELY DREAM

